  work wilson 's best known plays are fences ( 1985 ) ( which won a pulitzer prize and a tony award ) , the piano lesson ( 1990 ) ( a pulitzer prize and the new york drama critics ' circle award ) , ma rainey 's black bottom , and joe turner 's come and gone .

